<div id="pf1cc7" class="pf w33 h1e0" data-page-no="1cc7"><div class="pc pc1cc7 w33 h1e0"><div class="t m3b0 xcf h22 y1f34 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 1 for October 3, 1936 </div><div class="t mb25 x83 h3a y20ba ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY LESSON STUDY: </div><div class="t m41e x77 h2f y20a1 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Place a check mark in the proper space. </div><div class="t mf2 x4a h3a y6f7 ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUNDAY </div><div class="t m5 x63 h3a yc75 ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m1ca3 x35 h2f y6f7 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MONDAY I </div><div class="t m121a x69 h3a y735 ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">TUESDAY I WEDNESDAY I THURSDAY I FRIDAY I SABBATH </div><div class="t m1ee x3e h31 y9eb ff1 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Word—Its Origin, Inspiration, and Purpose </div><div class="t m7ab x3e h2f yff1 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY VERSE: &quot;All scripture is given by inspiration of God, and is profitable </div><div class="t m6a4 x48 h2f ycfe ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for doctrine, for reproof, for correction, for instruction in righteousness : that the </div><div class="t m1471 x48 h2f y12c7 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man of God may be perfect, throughly furnished unto all good works.&quot; 2 Tim. </div><div class="t m110b x48 h2f y73d ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3:16, 17. </div><div class="t ma6 x3e h2f ya88 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">STUDY HELP: &quot;The Great Controversy,&quot; Introduction, pp. v-viii. </div><div class="t me5d x69 h22 ycd2 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Origin of the Scriptures </div><div class="t m7a0 x73 h32 ydf5 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m197 x4e h32 y9f1 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">After the entrance of sin, how did God speak to the ancient fa-</div><div class="t m44 x3e h32 y12cd ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thers? Heb. 1:1. </div><div class="t m571 x5d h4 yf29 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.—In man&apos;s innocence in Eden, God spoke with him face to face; but </div><div class="t ma4b x16 h4 yd72 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">since sin entered God has sent His messages through chosen men. </div><div class="t mec2 x73 h32 y1275 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m3e1 x28 h32 y109c ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What simple term does our Lord use for the entire Old Testament? </div><div class="t m82d x3e h32 y14e8 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What importance did He attach to these writings? John 5:39. </div><div class="t mfd x73 h2f y1575 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;During </div><div class="t mb7f xcf h4 y1179 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the first twenty-five hundred years of human history, </div><div class="t m33d x16 h4 y7f7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there was no written revelation. Those who had, been taught of God, com-</div><div class="t ma75 x16 h4 yd09 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">municated their knowledge to others, and it was handed down from father </div><div class="t ma78 x16 h4 ya93 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to son, through successive generations. The preparation of the written word </div><div class="t m26a x16 h4 yc7c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">began in the time of Moses. Inspired revelations were then embodied in an </div><div class="t m635 x16 h4 y895 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inspired book. This work continued during the long period of sixteen hundred </div><div class="t m66e x16 h4 ycad ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">years, from Moses, the historian of creation and the law, to John, the recorder </div><div class="t m17d x3e h4 yf3d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the most sublime truths of the gospel.&quot;—&quot;The </div><div class="t mf3c x9f h30 yf3d ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy,&quot; Intro-</div><div class="t mb1d x16 h30 y11af ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">duction, p. v. </div><div class="t m55a x73 h4 y121e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Before the oldest of the world&apos;s poets had sung, the shepherd of Midian </div><div class="t m7d0 x16 h4 y9bd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[Moses] recorded those words of God to </div><div class="t md8 x1f h30 y9bd ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job.&quot;—&quot;Education,&quot; p. 159. </div><div class="t maaa x73 h4 y15fc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is conclusive that our. Lord accepted the canon of the Old Testament, as </div><div class="t ma78 x3e h4 ye50 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">collected and compiled by Ezra, Nehemiah, and others,—for He cited these </div><div class="t m73f x16 h4 y11f5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">writings as of divine origin. </div><div class="t m2ca x48 h32 y573 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m200 x28 h32 y573 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What three groups of the Old Testament does the Saviour recog-</div><div class="t m7a8 x3e h32 y7e0 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nize? Luke 24:44. </div><div class="t mb90 x48 h32 y15fd ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t ma5 x28 h32 y15fd ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who is prominently mentioned among Old Testament writers? </div><div class="t m5cb x3e h32 y1c28 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Luke 16:31; 24:27. </div><div class="t mb90 x73 h32 yf0c ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m9e5 x4e h32 ycb3 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through whom did God give the law? John 1:17; 7:19; Matt. 8:4. </div><div class="t m9b x73 h32 y93d ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m4a8 x28 h32 yf51 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who of the prophets is especially mentioned by our Saviour? </div><div class="t mdbb x3e h32 yde6 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 24:15. </div><div class="t mb90 x48 h32 y1150 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m2a0 x28 h32 yed3 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From whose writings did Christ and the apostles frequently quote? </div><div class="t m1645 x3e h32 ybe2 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Luke 20:42, 43; Acts 1:20; 13:33. </div><div class="t m7f7 x73 h32 y1548 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m9ba x28 h32 ybe3 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Jesus say would enable the apostolic teachers and </div><div class="t m2c7 x3e h32 y993 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">writers to testify accurately concerning Himself? John 14:26. </div><div class="t m426 x73 h4 y943 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—The Holy Spirit brought to mind the sayings and miracles of our </div><div class="t m7e1 x16 h4 yb00 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord with accuracy, that succeeding generations might have the testimony of </div><div class="t m12e8 x9a h69 y13a6 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[</div><div class="t m3944 x1e h3a y13a5 ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">41 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
